• Strategy : 
	1️⃣ Go to the LinkedIn search bar and type “job referrals.”

	2️⃣ Filter by Posts and sort by Latest.

	3️⃣ You’ll find posts by individuals or companies offering job referrals.

• Cold Referral message Template :

Hi [Name],

I can across [Job title] at [Company] and feel it aling with my skills. Could you refer me or advise on applying? I'd greatly value your support.

Thank you!

